    "Appendix A.4 provides further detail on guidelines, recruitment, and task framing.",
    "Position Bias SensitivityIn the Full Context experiment results ( Table 3: Joint Scores of LLMs in the Full Context Setting, based on how documents are sorted.",
    "Documents can be in Random order or sorted such that relevant ones are at the Top or Bottom of the context window.dered arbitrarily, with relevant documents in the top, middle, and bottom portions of the context window.",
    "Prior work (Huang et al., 2023; Chang et al., 2023; Chen et al., 2023b; Ravaut et al., 2023) has reported that models exhibit a position bias that leads them to put more importance on information in the context window's extremities.",
